Or use this:
<code><pre>:-moz-autofill, :autofill, :-moz-autofill-preview {
  filter: unset
}</pre></code>
 in file <a href="http://kb.mozillazine.org/UserContent.css" title="http://kb.mozillazine.org/UserContent.css"><b>userContent.css</b></a>.

style.css:
/* css for Stylus / xStyle / Stylish */

@supports (filter: revert) {
form input {
    filter: none
}

}

/* works only from userContent.css file:
:-moz-autofill, :autofill, :-moz-autofill-preview {
  filter: unset
}
*/
